   <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id801720719053403">Click on a panel heading (E.g. "Format") to expand or collapse the panel.</paragraph>
   <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id251721753273095">The (â˜°) icon next to the panel heading opens the <link href="text/swriter/01/05040000.xhp"><menuitem>Page Style</menuitem></link> dialog.</paragraph>
   <paragraph role="note" id="par_id301720717531972">The Page deck provides quick access to basic page style options. Use the <link href="text/swriter/01/05040000.xhp"><menuitem>Page Style</menuitem></link> dialog to access advanced page style options.</paragraph>
